::Fidgit::

She wadled along in her otter mode alone the lake shore.  She turned her ear 
to hear the sounds of lazar blasts and missles exploding.
She stood up o her hind liegs and looked around.
"No one here.  I wonder where all the rachet is coming from. Well, there is 
only one way to find out."

She turned away from the lake and towards the sourse of all the noises.
She sniffed the air and kept heading to the noise.

"I know my curiosity has gotten the better of me.  I'd be safer if I stayed 
at the lake.  But, I just got to find out what is going on."
